body:
Adjust fishing times.

```
{
    // range for fish travel time, in ticks
    "fishTravelTimeRange": [
        20,
        80
    ],

    // range for wait time, in ticks
    "waitTimeRange": [
        100,
        600
    ],

    // amount each lure level decreases the wait time, in ticks
    "lureLevelFactor": 100
}
```
**default values are set to vanilla
